
Please read the documentation in doc/mkprom2.pdf.

Linux, cygwin:
-------------
Install to /opt/mkprom2. Add /opt/mkprom2 to your PATH
$export /opt/mkprom2:$PATH
so that /opt/mkprom2/mkprom2 is accessible.

Windows:
-------
Install to c:/opt/mkprom2. Add c:/opt/mkprom2 to your PATH
so that c:/opt/mkprom2/mkprom2.exe is accessible.
